{"tid":1470054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"20190814蘋果：《環時》記者係黑工兼逾期逗留？","createTime":"2019-08-14T04:02:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T04:58:13.000Z","uid":220799,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a0e0d38dc7c802ca91336796256f351bf57dd5a3","tid":1470054,"uid":220799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:02:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">【逆權運動】《環時》記者係黑工兼逾期逗留？ 官媒力塑受迫害英雄形象</span><br />\n<br />\n中共喉舌《環球時報》旗下記者付國豪，於接近今日凌晨零時，在香港機場遭抗爭者包圍及制服，《環時》胡錫進隨即於零時44分發微博，指付「此次赴港除了報道，沒有任何其他任務」。不過，有網民從拍有付證件的照片中發現，他獲批逗留至2019年8月13日，且是以「訪客」身份入境香港，據香港入境事務處網頁的資料，訪客不能在香港接受有薪或無薪的工作，質疑他是逾期居留，更可能是「黑工」。<br />\n<br />\n付國豪因拒絕回答抗爭者是否記者，也沒有出示記者證，被質疑假冒記者，並意圖令抗爭者誤會他是內地執法部門卧底，引誘抗爭者包圍和制服他，挑起衝突。凌晨零時44分，胡錫進即在微博上發報消息，證實付是《環時》記者，並指他「在香港機場被示威者非法拘押，並遭到非人道的對待。」而他「此次赴港除了報道，沒有任何其他任務」。<br />\n<br />\n4分鐘後，環球網官方微博轉發胡錫進有關微博，並高調讚揚付是英雄，特別引述了付所說「我支持香港警察，你們可以打我了」這句話，並標籤了「付國豪真漢子」。零時58分，另一黨媒《人民日報》也轉發胡的微博，並引述「我支持香港警察，你們可以打我了」這句話，同樣標籤了「付國豪真漢子」。<br />\n<br />\n今晨7時50分左右，胡再發微博，指付「已經完全安全了」，同時藉此事大罵在暴力示威的現場圍攻、迫害記者，這是多麼無恥而懦弱的行徑，又指「激進示威者」野蠻並進行人身迫害，「我們是不是真的應該不再喊你們暴徒，而要改稱你們『恐怖分子』了？」<br />\n<br />\n《人民日報》海外版也發表了評論員文章，批評某些人鼓吹違法達義，標榜用違法手段，實現個人或團隊利益訴求的合理性，邏輯荒謬滑稽。任何主張，無論自認為目標有多麼崇高，都不能以違法的方式表達，更不能訴諸暴力。文章指，一個多月來，愛國愛港陣營無畏無懼、挺身而出，連續舉辦守護香港、支持警隊的活動，到警署探望慰問，為警察加油打氣，呼籲拒絕暴力，維護法治，恢復安寧，代表香港社會真正的主流民意。<br />\n<br />\n兩喉舌不停以跟進報道形式抺黑抗爭者，並將付塑造成受迫害的英雄形象，隨即引來內地大批網民對抗爭者的口誅筆伐。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，拍有付國豪證件及入境標籤的現場照片流出，有眼尖的香港網民發現，入境標籤上標明付國豪於2019年8月6日入境香港，獲批逗留時間至2019年8月13日。而他於約凌晨零時仍出現在機場，或已違反了入境條例，屬於過期逗留。此外，入境標籤亦標明，付以訪客身份入境。而根據香港入境處網頁上資料，香港法例《入境規例》（第115A章）第2（1）條的規定，給予某人以訪客身份在香港入境的准許，須受逗留條件規限，當中包括「不得接受有薪或無薪的僱傭工作」，故付若真的是在機場內進行採訪，可能已違規，屬於黑工。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff7b9a3501e5b74731a10fa5d020939a8abcda89","tid":1470054,"uid":220799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:04:47.000Z","msg":"自推十連<br />\n612 721 811 818"},{"pid":"454940b458f1d119d22c6f4e393b66d93e9f6512","tid":1470054,"uid":220799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:04:58.000Z","msg":"612 721 811 818"},{"pid":"2aca5dee3cc20adc9f9e2202a430df40726bcc6a","tid":1470054,"uid":281567,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a9202b1be74a520f2813e31d84492883b13071","tid":1470054,"uid":220799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:05:25.000Z","msg":"612 721 811 818"},{"pid":"86eec9a969fa4f06e7ccc668b7a49a80a08a9f11","tid":1470054,"uid":220799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:05:35.000Z","msg":"612 721 811 818"},{"pid":"e7e36e00849e3a130531e067713f258c5c8e377b","tid":1470054,"uid":220799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:05:45.000Z","msg":"612 721 811 818"},{"pid":"4c097ff339c25a2dc774a0d4a0e38c002dbfe7a8","tid":1470054,"uid":220799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:05:57.000Z","msg":"612 721 811 818"},{"pid":"f9cf007bebaa248fee03c606e26bb6b8b1ce6dc6","tid":1470054,"uid":220799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:06:10.000Z","msg":"612 721 811 818"},{"pid":"58fe18bb111ee59817ffdff8ecbf06c29d5306f7","tid":1470054,"uid":220799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:06:24.000Z","msg":"612 721 811 818"},{"pid":"98b5a859a1bde88da3572c7602b60e5bf2ad7aa7","tid":1470054,"uid":220799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:06:36.000Z","msg":"612 721 811 818"},{"pid":"9137a8c0ad0095515d9c8ae0691a2f835904454a","tid":1470054,"uid":220799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:06:49.000Z","msg":"612 721 811 818"},{"pid":"d30738a6b871a5405e89c19bccd6c725c256d977","tid":1470054,"uid":143151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2aca5dee3cc20adc9f9e2202a430df40726bcc6a","tid":1470054,"uid":281567,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:06:53.000Z","msg":"佢有係香港做採訪<br />\n環時 話佢係派港記者<br />\n但因為佢係遊客 冇申請 所以任何有糧冇糧Job都唔做得"},{"pid":"5e37a7776c32da36d799af0a7f7dd5c57d17cc9e","tid":1470054,"uid":220799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:07:03.000Z","msg":"612 721 811 818"},{"pid":"e0d3781cb73b1f2da13fdabf1b1a1b201cbbc59b","tid":1470054,"uid":79878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2aca5dee3cc20adc9f9e2202a430df40726bcc6a","tid":1470054,"uid":281567,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:07:03.000Z","msg":"只係解釋到佢過期居留<br />\n都係黑工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64dfbf0b79063eb1f14f0ed94b5eb0f91de3d5fb","tid":1470054,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52bc175fb4af56d58bec2c1ee042476eebc7bd7","tid":1470054,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d30738a6b871a5405e89c19bccd6c725c256d977","tid":1470054,"uid":143151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2aca5dee3cc20adc9f9e2202a430df40726bcc6a","tid":1470054,"uid":281567,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:06:53.000Z","msg":"佢有係香港做採訪<br />\n環時 話佢係派港記者<br />\n但因為佢係遊客 冇申請 所以任何有糧冇糧Job都唔做得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:08:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5535702705ffd04e647c6132e7aaad049d1dbe2c","tid":1470054,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:08:30.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"24c7f7cb74ec4bce016b92938e5bab73456d28aa","tid":1470054,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:08:51.000Z","msg":"因為佢有可能參與荃灣斬人<br />\n<br />\n所唔拎工作簽證來港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8a65ef73099d1662ee5b037282d9c6a912e003","tid":1470054,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:09:19.000Z","msg":"大家停一停，唔好再話自己手足喇。。激動既有佢激動既原因，加上星期日之後有邊個唔嬲呀？大家可唔可以係唔同身份角度諗下呢？大家都係香港人，矛頭都係一致，對準政府呀！！唔該大家理智d諗諗再行動，其實有冇鬼都係一樣，睇返場合睇返當時既形勢處境，亦都係旅客個角度去諗下啦。尋日我地真係有唔岩既地方架，試諗下尋日d機係未取消既情況，旅客delay佢地上唔到機，班機照飛，錢照袋，旅客比左錢冇得搭機係咪會燥呀？？唔該各位手足理性少少，唔好比d唔理性既人帶到啦。。既然我地人手唔夠多，做唔到癱瘓行動，咁咪轉第二個策略，做宣傳，等夜晚多d手足入黎做返前一日做既野囉，而家比人唔理性既帶風向做過激既事，你覺得邊個最開心呀？林鄭呀！！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">btw重點：唔好再話自己手足喇，咁做都做左，一齊諗下計點解決／舒緩呢件事啦好冇？</span></span></strong><br />\n仲有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">獨立思考</span></strong></span>！！大家都係聰明人，比我聰明100倍都唔止。"},{"pid":"7d9154a0d36effeec57ce01bddb9afda6f841699","tid":1470054,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:09:25.000Z","msg":"omg"},{"pid":"5621a5b619b8fd8f3a4e6ae0dab85d40ed604c9e","tid":1470054,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:09:51.000Z","msg":"[公投] 817機場or紅土?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463062\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463062</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">612 721 811</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WEc7HxV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWEc7HxV.jpg&h=bc18cb82&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jNxu1GJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjNxu1GJ.jpg&h=64932c27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WVOuhe4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWVOuhe4.jpg&h=a6d636f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MVCGSoB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMVCGSoB.jpg&h=085d041c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71f0778f7867ddf388f9d47c80cba5c04b2cb269","tid":1470054,"uid":174767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d30738a6b871a5405e89c19bccd6c725c256d977","tid":1470054,"uid":143151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2aca5dee3cc20adc9f9e2202a430df40726bcc6a","tid":1470054,"uid":281567,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:06:53.000Z","msg":"佢有係香港做採訪<br />\n環時 話佢係派港記者<br />\n但因為佢係遊客 冇申請 所以任何有糧冇糧Job都唔做得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:11:19.000Z","msg":"之前咪有同樣既CASE，個台灣COSPLAY俾人影相拉鳩左"},{"pid":"17a1a9755dd6db6628dd3c80a7a231b903067a5c","tid":1470054,"uid":190629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:15:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc0d9add6263b7ed17997d8e861923756e27acd7","tid":1470054,"uid":61547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score